              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>All hematological parameters are within normal limits except for a markedly elevated platelet distribution width (PDW), which may indicate increased platelet size variability, possibly reflecting platelet activation or increased turnover. No evidence of anemia, leukopenia, or thrombocytopenia. Correlate PDW finding clinically; consider repeating if clinically indicated or if there are symptoms suggestive of hematological or inflammatory disorders.</td></tr></table></div>"
